{"tid":741733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"名校生突破養兒防老災傳統，大義滅親","createTime":"2018-07-14T02:57:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T06:03:15.000Z","uid":183708,"like":343,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"cf7556a5df48ee4c1e20ba9201fb3a020e3f993b","tid":741733,"uid":183708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T02:57:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180714&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20449619\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180714%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20449619&d=QWEDxSi9giyc4bMK95eNSwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=5585be28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180714%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20449619&h=dc89ccf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20180714&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20449619</a><br />\n<br />\n仔賣養老屋　父︰攬住一齊死<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n【本報訊】年近七旬老父稱遭兩名喇沙書院畢業的忤逆子，瞞住他賣走「養老屋」，日前入稟與兩子爭產。老父昨接受《蘋果》專訪指兩子嗜財如命，為賣樓套現「老竇都唔認」。老父擬舉報任職銀行及曾任職股票行的兩子曾為騙取銀行按揭虛報職業，「攬住一齊死，唔可以畀佢哋逍遙法外！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吳國樑欲揭發兩子為騙按揭虛報職業。<br />\n<br />\n斥為套現「老竇都唔認」<br />\n<br />\n69歲原告吳國樑指，2009年以兩子吳宇軒、吳宇光（34及32歲）名義買入涉案將軍澳維景灣畔養老屋後，前年再買入同區海天晉兩單位。吳踢爆兩子當時失業，但<span style=\"color: red;\">為了上會，二人刻意考取的士牌，三父子同聲稱任職的士司機月入3萬元，成功獲批500萬元按揭貸款。</span><br />\n<br />\n吳父自稱草根出身，早年是市政局公務員，「睇住曾蔭權第一日返工」。為助兩子入喇沙小學，他樓換樓遷往九龍塘。<span style=\"color: red;\">「諗住個仔一定會養老竇」</span>的吳父痛斥兩子比電視劇《深宮計》的太平公主更奸，二人嗜財如命，前年游說末期肺癌母親立遺囑，由兩兄弟繼承物業業權。三父子曾為病危的妻子和母親彈琴溫馨獻唱生日歌，如今卻成仇敵。吳父稱，他得悉兩子出售維景灣畔物業時，上門被保安阻撓，幼子報警，更當眾說「呢個唔係我老竇」。現居的海天晉單位也是兒子持有，吳父擔心對方會將單位賣掉，無家可歸。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCA1615/18<br />\n■採訪羅日昇、撰文伍嘉豪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n養兒防老正仆街"},{"pid":"8bb6e4320cd630c376d2e65271f13ea8a505f1f0","tid":741733,"uid":51920,"like":193,"dislike":2,"score":191,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T03:55:15.000Z","msg":"連自住樓都落個仔名 <br />\n係仆街就賣埋佢<br />\n等你訓街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c60ac4be2138409952bb4aa1a670a01a8bed4c","tid":741733,"uid":183708,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8bb6e4320cd630c376d2e65271f13ea8a505f1f0","tid":741733,"uid":51920,"like":193,"dislike":2,"score":191,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T03:55:15.000Z","msg":"連自住樓都落個仔名 <br />\n係仆街就賣埋佢<br />\n等你訓街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T04:41:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"772767830ac47294ac6c7a6d782174c47248a8c1","tid":741733,"uid":121580,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T04:47:03.000Z","msg":"虛報職業銀行可以多數即追數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n政府都唔一定會告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家講返根本無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f44d4e9f995b42fdfec00215a644a81ef8fc4b","tid":741733,"uid":29314,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T04:48:30.000Z","msg":"tvb拿拿聲拍返套劇啦"},{"pid":"2eee4b797eb26a9e57321acff9d2cbe3d7b798e4","tid":741733,"uid":79563,"like":265,"dislike":3,"score":262,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T04:51:07.000Z","msg":"廢老無講邊個供樓？<br />\n<br />\n佢比3成首期, 仔供7成, 點計都係仔大份<br />\n<br />\n等阿媽走左先郁佢, 可見兩個仔好鍚阿媽, 好撚憎個老豆"},{"pid":"02fe06a20fa39d8da923a2a50a6449f9b0eff73c","tid":741733,"uid":79563,"like":178,"dislike":0,"score":178,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T04:52:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吳父稱，他得悉兩子出售維景灣畔物業時，上門被保安阻撓，幼子報警，更當眾說「呢個唔係我老竇」。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩個仔真係好憎佢老豆"},{"pid":"3cfdf643d616761c99c9f6f4067203f338630bdb","tid":741733,"uid":79563,"like":102,"dislike":0,"score":102,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T04:53:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前年游說末期肺癌母親立遺囑，由兩兄弟繼承物業業權。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能三母子睇得出佢老豆仆街, 所以咁做"},{"pid":"7bd499487a713fd3c96902875cce0a4a633dee6a","tid":741733,"uid":79563,"like":118,"dislike":1,"score":117,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T04:54:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>養兒防老正仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n養兒防老正係成功既, <br />\n<br />\n佢地阿媽得享天年, 兩個仔照顧到佢走左, 先同老豆反面"},{"pid":"543cf0461c0b9382fdbccae2226d2e834c9f5a83","tid":741733,"uid":183708,"like":315,"dislike":4,"score":311,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T07:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/153233_21e2f277f172263427dea488a4591877.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F153233_21e2f277f172263427dea488a4591877.png&h=d6e1aa9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無神論的巴別塔講得幾好<br />\n有因必有果"},{"pid":"0d5adcfaa40f7cc40fa2554e5e93c135e4db2ba6","tid":741733,"uid":54927,"like":75,"dislike":0,"score":75,"quote":{"pid":"543cf0461c0b9382fdbccae2226d2e834c9f5a83","tid":741733,"uid":183708,"like":315,"dislike":4,"score":311,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T07:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/14/153233_21e2f277f172263427dea488a4591877.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F14%2F153233_21e2f277f172263427dea488a4591877.png&h=d6e1aa9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無神論的巴別塔講得幾好<br />\n有因必有果"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T07:34:44.000Z","msg":"agree <br />\n無人會出世就咁仆街<br />\n一定係相處出左問題"},{"pid":"baaaa90479ebfe7049c0bb5ea66ddaa3b07b1c58","tid":741733,"uid":149342,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T07:36:13.000Z","msg":"正常公務員臨老都咁"},{"pid":"8253f0d103ce731972a1fc0ddd8191ca93afe6b2","tid":741733,"uid":26329,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T07:37:53.000Z","msg":"佢自己係咁教仔 佢自己都視財如命啦"},{"pid":"11f434ece7e3b46cb727e00da2cccaf03300b80b","tid":741733,"uid":164730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T07:40:21.000Z","msg":"喇沙佬做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da8a02b58cebf1218567aa2b233d4d09c391961","tid":741733,"uid":22553,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T07:44:58.000Z","msg":"谷到個仔入名校，緊係要佢搵多啲錢黎防老啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d81e98f8566ae2b8e2006a58a92357265a1c4a","tid":741733,"uid":75765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T07:53:52.000Z","msg":"鹿鼎記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e46e870d15fb2f38fd41c8fcfe9b17ccdec9923","tid":741733,"uid":121580,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T08:00:32.000Z","msg":"個老豆話個兩個仔每個月俾租<br />\n但個兩個仔只要話d錢係拎來供樓<br />\n個老豆就食得屎<br />\n個官肯定信個兩個仔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一開始銀行唔借錢俾個老豆,<br />\n借兩個仔個名買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又要兩個仔俾[租]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又想自己做實質業主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁撚大貪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最好跟返每人出幾多錢分返佢地<br />\n老豆俾首期,兩個仔有實名又有份供<br />\n正常一個分3份1就差唔多<br />\n一個唔好彩個老豆有可能一蚊都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e4a033ebcb2f7a98acc24774a038dd085bd06f","tid":741733,"uid":88886,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T08:07