撚有錢咩<br />\n<br />\n而老母知道佢爛賭先比遺產兩個仔 叫佢地養個老野<br />\n個老野想分翻錢去賭 所以<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963ecce91577280f9644ec409f16a05d7ac60db3","tid":741733,"uid":79823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T22:45:51.000Z","msg":"我信老母既決定<br />\n亦信兩個仔唔會同時都係仆街"},{"pid":"d2ac5a8cd2735a0d4dfe45cb169b808290e50477","tid":741733,"uid":56212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T00:38:46.000Z","msg":"三個都係人生勝利組<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有樓就代表成日嘆世界唔駛做<br />\n<br />\n失業?番工搵食先係孽"},{"pid":"1ddca5be6343258ffa38af3dfa0467e903878774","tid":741733,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T02:53:06.000Z","msg":"岩岩新聞話個老豆2006年破產,層樓2009年買入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nd錢邊度來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4b6283fc08de8941536d87deeadde5f81db57b7","tid":741733,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ddca5be6343258ffa38af3dfa0467e903878774","tid":741733,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T02:53:06.000Z","msg":"岩岩新聞話個老豆2006年破產,層樓2009年買入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nd錢邊度來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T05:22:14.000Z","msg":"咪靠老母平時收埋啲私己錢"}]}